    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Well-kept, honest car in good condition that\u2019s ready to be a comfortable, dependable daily driver. It presents nicely overall, has clearly been cared for, and offers a strong balance of value, condition, and usability. Expect normal signs of use for its age, but nothing that takes away from it being a solid, attractive vehicle.",
