      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A solid chance to pick up an honest project at an affordable price. This poor-condition car shows heavy wear and will need meaningful repair and sorting before it can be considered dependable, but for the right buyer it could be a worthwhile restoration, fixer-upper, or parts car. If you\u2019ve been looking for a budget-friendly entry point and don\u2019t mind putting in the work, this one has real potential.",
      "price": 4600.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an accessible way into dependable transportation at an attractive price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates straightforward value, whether as an economical daily driver, a backup vehicle, or a practical project. Offered as-is and priced to move, this is a smart opportunity for someone looking to maximize value without overpaying.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car is a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a handy backup vehicle, or a fun little project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s priced right for what it is and could be a great fit for the right buyer. If you\u2019re after value and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this one is definitely worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong-running powertrain feel and honest mechanical character. Starts, moves, and has the kind of usable drivetrain response that makes it worth saving. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but for the right buyer this is an affordable entry point with good bones for a daily, flip, or weekend fixer. Priced to move and a great value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
